.blue-prlx { position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px; height: 100%; width: 50%; }
h1, .h1 { font-size: 42px; line-height: 0.9; letter-spacing: 0.68px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
.bg-img-wrapper { background-color: rgb(2, 22, 37); flex-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 70px !important; }

.mobile-bg::before { content: ""; background: linear-gradient(rgba(2, 22, 37, 0) 0%, rgb(2, 22, 37) 81%, rgb(2, 22, 37) 100%) transparent; width: 100%; height: 67px; position: absolute; left: 0px; bottom: 0px; z-index: 0; }
.partners-section h3::before { content: ""; width: 60px; height: 5px; background-color: rgb(255, 209, 63); position: absolute; left: 0px; bottom: calc(100% + 11px); }
